<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>The Nutrition Science minor provides science students with a basic understanding of biochemical reactions involved in human metabolism, human organ systems, and an overview of nutrient functions, nutrient requirements, and metabolic regulation of nutritional pathways.</p>
]]>
</quickviewtext>
